sparse.eigenvolvers.java

Class SparseEigensolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • sparse.eigenvolvers.java.SparseEigensolver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Lobpcg

    public abstract class SparseEigensolver
extends java.lang.Object
    SEJ Java SparseEigensolver class.

    SEJ uses the MTJ Java library (matrix-toolkits-java) and Netlib Java (netlib-java) for numerical linear algebra and matrix computations.

    The SparseEigensolver abstract class provides class variables and methods that can be used to implement a general sparse eigenvalue solver.

    Author:
    Rico Argentati
